{"tid":1657021,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法後冇晒黑警","createTime":"2019-10-16T01:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T01:51:08.000Z","uid":206419,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43c020152c36da66acbc43306bcffe81a72c6cd6","tid":1657021,"uid":206419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:22:57.000Z","msg":"我地贏係國際上， 因為香港人示威係完全唔同其他國家既示威<span style=\"color: red;\">有目的、有原則、有秩序、有智慧［/red]，國際支持亦都係我地唯一贏到既手段，<br />\n跟住政府好大機會去全面抹黑示威者形象。<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊好可能會派人混入示威人士， 但目的唔再係拉人， 係[red]冇差別破壞、攻擊市民、搶劫燒燬商戶</span>。混入人數再唔係50～100， 可能係幾千或幾萬人。<br />\n<br />\n唔會再有黑警鏡頭出現， 所有既「差人」會安份地維持秩序，而所有既黑警與武警將會著既黑衫扮演着不同人士。<br />\n<br />\n就算捉到， 狗高層只會答係個別休班警員放工後既行為， 與政府冇關。 <br />\n<br />\n如果對方咁做， 人權法唔會制裁到高層，最多只會凍結condom仔同唔俾佢移民。<br />\n<br />\n扮演破壞呢招對家不嬲有用但只係試水溫同做俾藍絲睇， 嚟緊對國際就唔同講法。"},{"pid":"4593073dab053ede2fc214d92ce531e92b36584a","tid":1657021,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8b4f205de9289deddcd3e43e8ce08fbbcb20c418","tid":1657021,"uid":206419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"我咁撚蠢都諗到， 我相信對家一早諗到"},{"pid":"e02a7d1c3b7aa3a3841ec383be53c2dd0bcb3e98","tid":1657021,"uid":206419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"咁快就有負評， 三毛咁早起身返工呀"},{"pid":"d99c46e838a453a8f76b1179061451b77bc3eec8","tid":1657021,"uid":206419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfNpj7U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNpj7U.png&h=f6734468&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15R16NV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15R16NV.png&h=ddfcc7dc&s={SIZE}\" /